displayName: Sacred Sanctuary of the Divine Tree

parameters: Haa haa... Ah... K-Konoha-dono... Have you come...
I'm sorry, Demetri. It's because of me...

I'm glad you're safe... But more importantly...
Mari Mari-sama and Hardis

Kuh... Could you please help us defeat Hardis, for
the sake of us who are so useless, Konoha-san?

Understood. I'll leave Rudia to you, Demetri. I'm
heading towards Mari Mari-sama's support.

\c[10]Hardis, the Dark Lord\c[0] Oh... Is that
so... To rule over the Village of the Divine Tree
with such strength, how incredibly arrogant...

To desecrate the sacred sanctuary... You shall
witness the true power of my Alraune,
unforgivable!

Hardis, the Dark Lord: Laughable! I'm tired of
your feeble attacks! I will make you all die,
Marimari!

Mari Mari-sama, please don't do anything reckless.
You are an important leader here.

Oh! A magical girl... Are you here to help me,
Mari...?!

Of course. I will defeat this demon, Mari Mari-
sama, please step back.

I'm sorry...! It's reassuring to have a magical
girl... I'm counting on you, Konoha!

So, you came here to help Rudia by defeating the
Dark Lord Hardis...

\c[10]Hardis, the Dark Lord\c[0], seems to be more
capable than I thought... Was the information
about Belzevia true... Tch.

What are you blabbering about? Are you getting
scared, by any chance?

I'm sorry, but I can't just hand over this sacred
sanctuary to you, Dark Lord Hardis. Prepare
yourself.

\c[10]Dark Lord Hardis\c[0], you shamelessly mock
me... I will make you realize the power of the
Four Heavenly Kings.

I will make Dark Lord Hardis regret
underestimating me as a magical girl!

\c[10]Dark Lord Hardis\c[0] Guhaaa... Wha... What
kind of power is this...?!
Now, it's the end... Accept your fate.

\c[10]Dark Lord Hardis\c[0] You fool... I am
immortal... Dark Lord Hardis...! How
unfortunate...! Magical girl!

Such foolishness... There was a sense of
accomplishment...! But why...?!

Konoha, it's not like that. We can't defeat
this... we can't defeat it with just this. I
thought it might work out, but it seems like it's
no good after all...

Hardis and I are inseparable. Long ago, our
personalities split and became two separate
beings. But as long as one of us exists, the other
will never die...
W...What did you say...? Then, are you...

Don't worry, I'm not a demon myself. Originally,
both of us were human...

The great sage Harry Diswell... Once renowned as a
person with a dual personality... But due to the
rampage of their personality, one side became
demonized...

Yeah. Even though it's a fact that only Marimari-
sama knew, they have always supported me.

Today, Konoha, we can repay everything. To defeat
that person...

Stop it, Leedis! What will happen to Shirohana?
Who will deliver it? Who will make that flower
bloom?

Don't worry, I have left behind clear
instructions. Someone will be able to take my
place.

\c[10]Leedis\c[0], what are you saying, brother...
Could it be... you...?

Konoha-san, thank you for helping everyone. Thank
you all for everything until now. Goodbye.
※閃光とともに、ハーディス、リーディス消滅

......Leedis... I didn't want to lose you... Is
this also fate...

\c[10]Hardis, the Demon King\c[0] Hahaha! I've
defeated you, magical girl! Hmph, you're not as
strong as you claim to be...

\c[10]Hardis, the Demon King\c[0] With this, the
sacred village will become mine. Now, let's reveal
all the secrets of the sanctuary.
